flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Set counter to 0]
    B --> C[Loop through files in directory]
    C --> D{Filename contains a space?}
    D -- No --> H{More files?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Replace spaces with underscores]
    E --> F[Rename file with mv]
    F --> G[Increment counter]
    G --> H
    H -- Yes --> C
    H -- No --> I[Print files renamed]
    I --> J[Exit]
